data.description: This is a great opportunity for you to call a 3 bedroom, 2 bath home your own. The open floor plan features a large kitchen with plenty of counter space, a spacious living room, tile in the wet areas, and a sizeable laundry room. Your home also includes a backyard that is perfect for gardening and gatherings. You'll have plenty of parking space, too! This home is conveniently located just minutes from Downtown Houston, with easy access to major freeways. Don’t miss out, come see your home!
